{"tid":640944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓港對決]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強首回合--IU 對 謝安琪","createTime":"2018-04-24T16:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T04:59:27.000Z","uid":92376,"like":145,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"664e1ba48699bbb52088b34e4936b53da9cc1a6a","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"以下為馬上舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可直接以正負評功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIU v 謝安琪<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-24 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Y6Bfi0S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FY6Bfi0S.png&h=7c2b2042&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zCo0EEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzCo0EEy.png&h=fb8364fd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sbXOEPJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsbXOEPJ.png&h=db4323d3&s={SIZE}\" />IU v 謝安琪<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0Q6FBnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Q6FBnk.png&h=d7f5937a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以正負評功能投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的正負評功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"df0f54a15977b9050f5a221836a58c2fb7c4d74c","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"百密一疏,未改日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家照投啦,無謂咁都重開啦"},{"pid":"4b8bc30e541b729f40bfe5b9971d2005f1bfa85b","tid":640944,"uid":68320,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:01:42.000Z","msg":"IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ebe523882f1bdedee4fb51cc4fe071faad9d76","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"完爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6bd9d849ff2ef3a5c856fb2c544f1194ba900a","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"IU展示出要入決賽既無比決心<br />\n開賽五分鐘已經領先9分啦"},{"pid":"736b2ef5c989be6e51936fde0f93bf8522fb75ba","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"10分"},{"pid":"2593c84ea8b115dde1b5bfa66b9f1e45f4bba77c","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"謝安琪毫無還擊之力,無助既佢就好似身處印度或者台灣咁,等待暴雨過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d80cf58de34bc708a87a6c07f96a10425a429d6","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:06:42.000Z","msg":"好彩都仲有好心人助攻左2分比謝安琪<br />\n但落後咁多,應該難以追近啦"},{"pid":"71f17bb67ca35dd5f21b2fab0e48c5289abe3d40","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db70803c0721022fd9ffbb80e16b2528a4ef3d7","tid":640944,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img